Subject: [PATCH 04/18] fix(P2): replace 4 phantom palettes with design tokens
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- KeyFactors.tsx: CATEGORY_COLORS hex → cat-service/mental/global/return tokens
- MatchesTab.tsx: SURFACE_COLORS hex → accent-green/live/accent-blue/text-tertiary tokens
- MatchesTab.tsx: 2 fallbacks '#94a3b8' → 'var(--color-text-tertiary)'
- StanceBadge.tsx: STANCE_COLORS hex → mma-dec/ko/sub tokens, fallback tokenized
- StyleMatchupBadge.tsx: brawler/all_rounder hex → mma-brawler/mma-allrounder tokens
---
 frontend/src/components/KeyFactors.tsx            | 12 ++++++------
 frontend/src/components/MatchesTab.tsx            | 12 ++++++------
 frontend/src/components/mma/StanceBadge.tsx       |  8 ++++----
 frontend/src/components/mma/StyleMatchupBadge.tsx |  4 ++--
 4 files changed, 18 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

